        <num>CC 805</num>
        <heading>805.  Disposition of undivided share</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 805.  Disposition of undivided share
A co-owner may freely lease, alienate, or encumber his share of the thing held in indivision.  The consent of all the co-owners is required for the lease, alienation, or encumbrance of the entire thing held in indivision.</p>
        </content>
